Kimmeridge Energy (299 Resources) Fund III Co-Invest, LP  Financing
Kimmeridge Energy (299 Resources) Fund III Co-Invest, LP just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  This is a new filing. Kimmeridge Energy (299 Resources) Fund III Co-Invest, LP was able to sell $133,633,333. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 14 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $100,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-07-26. Kimmeridge Energy (299 Resources) Fund III Co-Invest, LP is based in  400 MADISON AVENUE, SUITE 14C  NEW YORK 10017. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  n/a Kimmeridge Energy Management Company GP, LLC.





